{"tid":1517553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[向白宮聯署反對曾偉雄入聯合國]又嚟啦！","createTime":"2019-08-30T03:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T08:24:51.000Z","uid":69473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ba44b37cd697634fbbd3023934a2aefa39ff1366","tid":1517553,"uid":69473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:05:38.000Z","msg":"係幾日前好多手足幫手聯署簽名，但因為被大陸仔hack聯署個網，所以無辦法再填。<span style=\"color: red;\">但當日手足好犀利，用左一日時間人數多左3萬幾個！大家延續呢團火啦好嘛</span><br />\n<br />\n上次個網過左期，懇請大家再填過！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-reject-nomination-andy-tsang-wai-hung-positions-united-nations\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-reject-nomination-andy-tsang-wai-hung-positions-united-nations&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8r7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=32b024f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-reject-nomination-andy-tsang-wai-hung-positions-united-nations</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">內容大意係指：<br />\n「大陸係6月份時提名 前香港警務處處長 曾偉雄 做 聯合國毒品和犯罪問題辦公室執行主任，就2014年時 曾偉雄 縱容警察濫暴及濫權。我哋認為個仆街唔合適坐上呢個高級職位，所以我哋聯署話俾世界知道！」</span><br />\n<br />\n請大家一齊幫手 填表 &gt; email收確認信 &gt; share開去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">記唔記得個仆街當年點對我哋，記唔記得當年七警依家點樣？仲係我哋出錢養緊班仆街呀當年警黑暴力就係由佢開始</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">懇求大家幫手，填完請幫推，share比朋友<br />\n懇求大家幫手，填完請幫推，share比朋友<br />\n懇求大家幫手，填完請幫推，share比朋友</span><br />\n<br />\n上個post :<br />\n向白宮聯署阻止曾偉雄入聯合國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1501147\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1501147</a>"},{"pid":"73498c47666119fe7449f5ae9baf5ee6a5bf6d0d","tid":1517553,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:05:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a h